  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Bandoneon bisonoric showcase — the engine's unique push/pull mechanic made explicit. Velocity threshold at 0.5 divides the keyboard into two timbral worlds: play soft (pull bank) for warm dual triangle oscillators with wide detune; play hard (push bank) for the triangle-saw blend that projects forward. Rapid alternation between soft and hard velocity creates the characteristic bellows-reversal breathing of real bandoneon technique. LFO2 at 0.6 Hz sweeps the filter between the two registers. The entanglement is internal: two instruments in one body.",
